       <h3> <a href="https://www.google.com/calendar/event?eid=NGhhb2gyYzJxa2w1bnVobHIyZ3U0NmNkNzAgZm9ydGVyaWVwbEBt&ctz=America/Toronto">
 
        Author visit: Deborah Ellis        </a></h3>
        <p class="small">
        Award-winning author and activist Deborah Ellis writes courageous and dramatic books that give Western readers a glimpse into the lives of children in war-torn and developing countries.  Ellis will be at the Crystal Ridge branch for a visit with students in grades 4-6 from St. George School.  Limited seating is available for the public, on a first-come basis.  Copies of several of Ellis' books will be available for sale and signing.</p>
    </div>

</div>
 
