            </div>
    <div class="col-sm-10 event-main">
       <h3> <a href="https://www.google.com/calendar/event?eid=cjRlN2l0Nm5tbDFjOGVqYzNmMWxrYjlxZzBfMjAxNjA1MDlUMTkwMDAwWiBmb3J0ZXJpZXBsQG0&ctz=America/Toronto">
 
        Homework Help        </a></h3>
        <p class="small">
        A free after-school program where tutors work with students in grades K - 8, helping with homework, study skills, and building confidence. Offered at Centennial and Crystal Ridge branches. To register or volunteer contact Janine Warren at jwarren@fepl.ca or 905-871-2546 x 311.</p>
    </div>

</div>
 
